LifeLock
Standard
™
Identity Theft Protection

Beyond credit monitoring, beyond what you can do by yourself.
Identity fraud can damage your finances, credit and reputation. Thieves can get a new home,
                car or line of credit in your name. At LifeLock, our job is to help protect against identity fraud and
                handle things for you if it occurs.






